    &trans       &trans    &trans     &uc_eyes   &uc_roll     &uc_thinking &uc_monkey     &trans         &trans         &uc_ohai         &uc_party &trans
    &trans       &trans    &uc_sweat  &trans     &uc_facepalm &trans       &uc_hug        &uc_joy        &uc_kiss       &uc_love         &trans    &trans
